sabagay, masarap kakurutan si mj: Just came back from Calaguas early this morning.  The beach was superb.   may mga tao pa din kahit sunday,  pero di ganun kadami.  sakto lang.  there was a time nasolo pa rin namin yung beach.  we arrived around lunch time on Sunday and based sa observation namin,  pinakamaganda ang view ng beach in terms of color and clarity of water kapag magtatanghali na.  It was light blue and the sea was very clear and calm.  Pag humahapon na kasi hindi na ganun kalight yung pagkablue niya pero maganda pa din.  thanks sa tips dito,  successful ang naorganize naming DIY Calaguas trip.  nanghinayang lang ako dahil di ako nakapagdala ng charger for my cam.  may outlet kasi yung cottage namin,  pede pala magcharge from 6pm to around 11pm.  about the condition ng dagat,  hindi ganun kalakas yung waves.  wisik wisik lang yung talsik ng tubig.  akala ko mahihilo ako at mababasa,  di naman pala.  Okay na okay ang weather condition.
